{"tid":1551533,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[埋大仔女同我入黎！！！] 理大罷課中期檢討問卷調查","createTime":"2019-09-08T04:58:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T14:38:38.000Z","uid":220045,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0093b68729a1ae1f8c91a733e29f9a15ef52cffc","tid":1551533,"uid":220045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:58:45.000Z","msg":"各位埋大手足：<br />\n<br />\n埋大罷課已經過左一星期，理大罷委想係連登做一個中期檢討問卷調查，徵詢各位埋大同學對罷課既意見，等我們能夠檢討未來同唔同單位共同籌辦罷課活動時有咩地方可以改善。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n是次問卷調查為不記名問卷，所有資料在中期檢討的程序完成後會予以銷毀。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeD83JKJNA9XEeovGpDMT4ScE0T6IoT37qOzEZRr0dNA80LvQ/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeD83JKJNA9XEeovGpDMT4ScE0T6IoT37qOzEZRr0dNA80LvQ%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprhyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=8870b22b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeD83JKJNA9XEeovGpDMT4ScE0T6IoT37qOzEZRr0dNA80LvQ/viewform?usp=sf_link</a><br />\n<br />\n謝謝各位埋大手足的支持！幫手推唔該！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef4b1c86ba549826b5717ac1dc2629dab39acdf","tid":1551533,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:03:43.000Z","msg":"今日<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係</span>唱fuck the popo <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係</span>唱毅進仔<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係</span>唱今天我 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今日係唱The Star-Spangled Banner</span>🇺🇸🇺🇸<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><sp